title: Salvador Dalí Apparition of face and fruit-dish on a beach Magnet
description:
Magnet developed from Salvador Dalí’s, Apparition of face and fruit-dish on a beach, 1938. © Salvador Dalí, Fundació Gala- Salvador Dalí / Artists Rights Society (ARS), New York, 2022.

Add some artistic flare to your magnetic surfaces with this masterpiece from our collection.

  • Single Magnet
  • Dimensions: 3.5 x 2.5 in.
